headline: Arch Capital: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: PEMBROKE, Bermuda (AP) — Arch Capital Group Ltd. (ACGL) on Monday reported third-quarter net income of $1.35 billion. On a per-share basis, the Pembroke, Bermuda-based company said it had profit of $3.56. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring gains, were $2.77 per share.
